# Bullet Bank
<!--
This file is normally generated automatically during onboarding
(or when you refresh your profile in the Coach tab), based on
your resume and conversation. You usually won't write this by
hand from scratch.

If you want to manually add or edit a bullet, follow the format
below — the AI reads this format when selecting bullets for a
tailored resume or outreach message.

bullet-bank.md is gitignored and will never be committed.

FORMAT:
- Bullets are organized by company, then grouped by theme within
  each company
- Each bullet is tagged with role-type tags (defined by you or
  generated based on your target roles) plus a priority:
  [primary] (strongest, most broadly applicable), [alt] (use if
  primary doesn't fit the job description), [optional] (only if
  the job description specifically calls for it)
- Bullets are written in their final, polished form — the AI
  uses them verbatim, it does not rewrite or paraphrase them
- The same achievement can have multiple bullet variants tagged
  for different role types if it should be framed differently
  depending on the job
-->

## How to Use This File

**Role type tags (example — define your own based on your target roles):**
- `[ops]` = Business Operations, Chief of Staff, Head of Operations
- `[strategy]` = Strategy, Corporate Development, Business Strategy
- `[finance]` = Finance, FP&A, Strategic Finance

**Priority tags:**
- `[primary]` = use this version first
- `[alt]` = use only if primary doesn't fit the job description
- `[optional]` = include only if the job description specifically calls for it

---

## Acme Corp | Senior Operations Manager
San Francisco, CA | January 2022 – Present

### Theme: Cross-Functional Process Improvement

- Redesigned the quarterly planning process across 6 business units, reducing cycle time by 40% and improving cross-functional alignment between product, sales, and finance `[ops][strategy][primary]`

- Led a cross-functional initiative spanning engineering, sales, and finance to redesign quarterly planning, cutting cycle time by 40% `[ops][alt]`

### Theme: Financial Planning

- Built a zero-to-one financial model for a new product line that informed a $12M investment decision and became the standard planning template for two subsequent launches `[finance][strategy][primary]`

- Partnered with finance leadership to build the company's first rolling 12-month forecast model, replacing static annual budgeting `[finance][alt]`

---

## Beta Industries | Strategy Associate
New York, NY | June 2019 – December 2021

### Theme: Market Analysis

- Built a market sizing model that reframed total addressable market for a Series B fundraise, contributing to a successful $40M raise `[strategy][finance][primary]`

- Conducted competitive analysis across 30+ companies in the vertical, identifying a positioning gap that informed the company's next two years of product roadmap `[strategy][optional]`

### Theme: Team Leadership

- Hired and onboarded a team of 5 analysts across 2 functions in 4 months during a period of rapid company growth `[ops][primary]`

- Coached 2 direct reports to promotion within 18 months through structured weekly 1:1s and stretch project assignments `[ops][optional]`
